  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe comply with the Family and Medical Leave Act (FMLA), which provides eligible individuals with job-protected leave for specific family and medical reasons. This includes leave for your own serious health condition, the care of a family member with a serious health condition, the birth or adoption of a child, and certain exigencies arising from a family member\u0027s military service. This policy outlines eligibility criteria, qualifying reasons for leave, notice requirements, and continuation of benefits during FMLA leave\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
